##DESCRIPTION
##  Online exam question for Right Triangle Trigonometry
##  Find the other sides and angles for a right triangle with two other parts given.
##ENDDESCRIPTION

## DBsubject(Trigonometry)
## DBchapter(Triangle trigonometry)
